message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech and audio processing. Other likely categories could be cs.CL (computational linguistics) as the paper deals with aligning lyrics to audio, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper uses non-negative matrix factorization and canonical time warping, cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper uses a computer vision technique for time warping, and cs.MM (multimedia) as the paper deals with aligning lyrics to audio in a multimedia context.
